moji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51eb1376b35ec78ab3fac7968b7a32e3376ca0b","tid":2171994,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:25:39.000Z","msg":"控方onL9，想用呢d砌得入既話就咬多d人"},{"pid":"d013d9a1a1d594e61f36681bd1a9009440442746","tid":2171994,"uid":37869,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"quote":{"pid":"87ddfa2ba56ba6c28bf02a1957180e858ce86bd1","tid":2171994,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":66,"score":-65,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:24:07.000Z","msg":"宜家啲官真係好驚會俾人制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:26:44.000Z","msg":"隻檢控官無啦啦喺到搞事 正常法官都嬲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明雙方都承認左的事實<br />\n控方又拎一大堆「證據」出黎拖時間"},{"pid":"6e999249d8d3e9111bf8ee0570c419af34558167","tid":2171994,"uid":124983,"like":54,"dislike":2,"score":52,"quote":{"pid":"87ddfa2ba56ba6c28bf02a1957180e858ce86bd1","tid":2171994,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":66,"score":-65,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:24:07.000Z","msg":"宜家啲官真係好驚會俾人制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:28:10.000Z","msg":"其實你呢d小學雞好撚煩 睇到好撚尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284aa53a7dc5fa48b43197592b63bcb92b5798ec","tid":2171994,"uid":354682,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"35bf5a6f9275fdc46c27cee3d6fe47fb261f6a66","tid":2171994,"uid":55317,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"3cf20af5acf617f15d6222687e76f479b6e37689","tid":2171994,"uid":240362,"like":188,"dislike":2,"score":186,"citedBy":3,